<h3>Intro&nbsp;</h3>
<p>India = one of oldest maritime civilisations (Chola used Malacca strait)</p>
<h3>Malacca and ANC (andamand and Nicobar)</h3>
<ol>
<li>strategic = 40% of INdian import via Malacca</li>
<li>Alternate to Malacca = Lombok route( 3 days extra ) , Singapore strait (too narrow :\)&nbsp;</li>
<li>ANC = natural outpost for India = vital role for maritime domain awareness as Hawk-eye&nbsp;</li>
<li>GSAT 7 satellite for MDA</li></ol>
<p>way forward&nbsp;</p>
<p>Malacca = gateway for Look East + Access to South China Sea + Pacific Ocean&nbsp;</p>
